ors que d’autres ont donné lieu à des épidémies plus localisées. Tourné vers l’avenir, ce livre propose des mesures de prévention et de gestion des futurs virus dangereux qui devraient émerger.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn French.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 02. Jun 2024) 7aMEDICAL / Laboratory Medicine.2bisacsh1 aRodney, Alan, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Plus PP Package 2023 Part 2z978311117804208iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2023z9783111318912oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Medicine and Life Sciences 2023z9783111318615oZDB-23-DPM08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEDP Sciences Frontlist eBook Package 2023z978311102379340uhttps://doi.org/10.1051/978-2-7598-3055-840uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9782759830558423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9782759830558/original  a978-3-11-102379-3  EDP Sciences Frontlist eBook Package 2023b2023  a978-3-11-117804-2  DG Plus PP Package 2023 Part 2b2023  aEBA_CL_MDPM  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_PPALL  aEBA_STMALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aZDB-23-DGGb2023  aZDB-23-DPMb2023